{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"24737-hippo-wants-to-dance","title":"Hippo Wants to Dance","description":"Hippo wants to dance. Won’t anyone dance with her?","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Marisa  Steyn ","Sam  Beckbessinger"],"illustrators":["Megan Andrews"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Book Dash","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/24737-hippo-wants-to-dance"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86908/size3/9e5f5a8635052315e4d550572471ac04.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86908/size6/9e5f5a8635052315e4d550572471ac04.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86077/size6/d11871eeabf964a696740246127d93ba.jpg","text":"2/25","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86078/size6/59a255f3581512e8d32d6e0a1d221e2c.jpg","text":"Hippo wants to dance.\nShe jumps up and down \non the dusty ground.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86079/size6/d3d538e58cf912b08dfd26824365db44.jpg","text":"THUMP!\nTHUMP!","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86080/size6/8baf182c7a7e096f1f8dcbe3b6180fec.jpg","text":"“You’re getting dirt on me!” says Shongololo, \nsleeping in the sand.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86081/size6/ece7ab88d64a48801128382f57fcf521.jpg","text":"“Go dance somewhere else.”","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86082/size6/4c24c0ac386e165cab07bc7e0ec33c55.jpg","text":"Hippo wants to dance. \nShe rolls into the river and \nsplashes her arms and legs.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86083/size6/79036500feec2641520d25711db324cf.jpg","text":"SPLISH! SPLASH!","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86084/size6/e4d168d13929b999ef12a89d863a08bc.jpg","text":"“You’re making me wet!” says Kingfisher, \nhunting for her breakfast.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86085/size6/a0fb4d23aa1e501a363c95a941be83a9.jpg","text":"“Go dance somewhere else.”","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86086/size6/c78d4d59d26ff2343b91d071754ea4d1.jpg","text":"Hippo wants to dance. \nShe twirls around and around in a field, \nkicking her legs up high.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86087/size6/f2ef8b66d6a994edc67a3fd02055e37f.jpg","text":"SWOOSH!\nSWOOSH!","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86088/size6/776135b6de08665a82ba1654fdc7749f.jpg","text":"“Be careful! You nearly kicked me!” \nsays Meerkat, bathing his babies.","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86089/size6/3cf00a284682ce204f267fec8aa4f7e2.jpg","text":"“Go dance somewhere else.”","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86090/size6/83e45e75c11da7d24f908fb7abafbb94.jpg","text":"Hippo wants to dance.\nShe flops into a puddle of mud and slides \naround on her nice big belly.","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86091/size6/8ccb33946b912cfdcd776b41f1f453cb.jpg","text":"SQUISH! SQUASH!","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86092/size6/4fdc238406103e4ffd46c7511b50b003.jpg","text":"“Why don’t you stop dancing?” asks Donkey, \ncarrying his buckets.","words":null},{"n":17,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86093/size6/a5197e3cd75618c700fa6847b181e7ea.jpg","text":"“Why can’t you do something useful instead?”","words":null},{"n":18,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86094/size6/6cfa37fed606c9a861329435e16d6d7f.jpg","text":"Hippo is sad.\nShe is too sad to dance.","words":null},{"n":19,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86095/size6/54d18c24882a528e3adc5b62c8a48998.jpg","text":"She sits on a rock and cries. \nThe tears roll down her cheeks and fall on the ground.","words":null},{"n":20,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86096/size6/f79087b16581a2dd7fe45572e93cec48.jpg","text":"PLOP!\nPLOP!\nGrasshopper hears Hippo’s tears. \nHe starts dancing around her feet.","words":null},{"n":21,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86097/size6/1d111c71276f6f03c20b5ec81b6b4b47.jpg","text":"HOP! HOP!","words":null},{"n":22,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86098/size6/ac35a9d7d073c14dbaf6dbf052e29cea.jpg","text":"Hippo and Grasshopper start to dance, and the other animals come to look …","words":null},{"n":23,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86099/size6/de93bd61bca6876c36d7f7b56efd64cd.jpg","text":"24/25","words":null},{"n":24,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86100/size6/a212ca46bd64640fca4799832847fbcd.jpg","text":"25/25","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":24,"words":191}}